How much more suffering must he endure?"

00:16:36.160 --> 00:16:36.960
Regardless of

00:16:37.390 --> 00:16:39.320
whether it's superstition or not,

00:16:39.790 --> 00:16:40.720
in the end,

00:16:40.790 --> 00:16:42.120
neither side objected,

00:16:42.320 --> 00:16:43.910
and the body was buried.

