A few years later,

00:16:47.790 --> 00:16:49.250
during the big crackdown,

00:16:49.510 --> 00:16:50.440
the Bao family

00:16:50.610 --> 00:16:52.070
was completely uprooted,

00:16:52.120 --> 00:16:53.790
along with Leader Zhao.

00:16:54.320 --> 00:16:55.580
They were all exposed.

00:16:55.750 --> 00:16:56.480
Later,

00:16:56.910 --> 00:16:58.260
he was released on medical parole,

00:16:58.260 --> 00:16:59.320
and not long after,

00:16:59.480 --> 00:17:00.200
he was gone.

00:17:01.320 --> 00:17:02.840
I regret that I couldn't personally

00:17:02.840 --> 00:17:04.640
catch those Bao family members.

00:17:07.160 --> 00:17:08.589
After the Xu Qingli case,

00:17:09.270 --> 00:17:11.869
I took medical retirement
the following year.

00:17:12.829 --> 00:17:13.690
Actually, I...

00:17:14.720 --> 00:17:16.720
I wanted to work for a few more years.

00:17:16.829 --> 00:17:18.550
Even if they had transferred me
to a less demanding position,

00:17:18.550 --> 00:17:20.680
I would have been willing to continue.

00:17:20.960 --> 00:17:22.359
But they wouldn't agree.

00:17:23.510 --> 00:17:25.440
A person's life is like a case file.

00:17:26.790 --> 00:17:27.510
About what you've accomplished

00:17:27.510 --> 00:17:28.710
and what you haven't,

00:17:30.640 --> 00:17:31.990
once the seal is stamped,

00:17:31.990 --> 00:17:33.450
that's the final verdict.

00:17:35.180 --> 00:17:36.420
But

00:17:36.720 --> 00:17:38.250
how many chances to be young

00:17:38.480 --> 00:17:39.880
do we get in life?

00:17:44.960 --> 00:17:45.350
Here.

00:17:45.880 --> 00:17:46.950
My name is Youth Xu.

00:17:48.240 --> 00:17:49.570
Youth without regrets.

