So I'm asking,
are you related through your sister

00:19:53.270 --> 00:19:54.350
or directly to the Bao family?

00:19:54.350 --> 00:19:55.240
It is

00:19:55.270 --> 00:19:56.110
not about that.

00:19:56.110 --> 00:19:57.200
Alright, alright.

00:19:57.270 --> 00:19:58.640
Go on. Continue.

