Well...

00:20:02.030 --> 00:20:03.070
I didn't want to

00:20:03.580 --> 00:20:05.180
get involved in this matter.

00:20:05.480 --> 00:20:06.700
It's because

00:20:06.750 --> 00:20:07.510
my sister and I,

00:20:07.510 --> 00:20:08.550
when we were on our trip,

00:20:08.550 --> 00:20:09.790
ran into Xu Qingli.

00:20:27.550 --> 00:20:28.230
Pull over.

00:20:29.580 --> 00:20:30.380
What's wrong?

00:20:31.520 --> 00:20:32.850
Let's go to Bao's house.

00:20:33.110 --> 00:20:33.880
Bao's house?

00:20:34.500 --> 00:20:35.700
Hurry!

00:20:37.510 --> 00:20:38.640
I need to turn around.

00:20:38.640 --> 00:20:39.640
You're so stupid.

00:20:42.330 --> 00:20:43.160
Hop in.

00:20:43.240 --> 00:20:44.790
Let's go, come on!

00:20:44.880 --> 00:20:45.750
Alright!

00:20:46.090 --> 00:20:47.210
Later, we

00:20:47.240 --> 00:20:49.000
couldn't catch up with Xu Qingli.

00:20:49.000 --> 00:20:49.720
Then,

00:20:50.070 --> 00:20:51.270
those people from the Bao family

00:20:51.270 --> 00:20:52.870
ended up staying at my house.

00:20:53.350 --> 00:20:54.240
They ate my food,

00:20:54.240 --> 00:20:56.200
lived in my house, and drank my drinks,

00:20:56.200 --> 00:20:57.790
and I couldn't kick out of them,
no matter what.

00:20:57.790 --> 00:20:59.480
I really had no choice.

00:20:59.550 --> 00:21:00.160
I...

00:21:01.110 --> 00:21:01.830
Officer.

00:21:02.310 --> 00:21:02.960
What I did

00:21:03.440 --> 00:21:04.700
is not illegal, right?

00:21:05.590 --> 00:21:06.590
It's not illegal,

00:21:06.590 --> 00:21:08.000
but it's not right either.

00:21:08.000 --> 00:21:09.440
It's not that I'm not right. I just...

00:21:09.440 --> 00:21:10.500
Alright, alright.

00:21:10.820 --> 00:21:12.420
Go on. Continue.

00:21:14.070 --> 00:21:15.210
The day before

00:21:15.240 --> 00:21:16.240
we found the body,

00:21:16.880 --> 00:21:19.200
my brother-in-law bought some liquor,

00:21:19.220 --> 00:21:21.000
and I drank with the Bao family members

00:21:21.000 --> 00:21:22.240
together.

00:21:22.310 --> 00:21:23.110
In the end,

00:21:23.200 --> 00:21:24.880
everyone passed out drunk.

00:21:25.640 --> 00:21:27.350
The next day,

00:21:27.440 --> 00:21:29.240
just before dawn,

00:21:29.310 --> 00:21:31.070
I felt uncomfortable

00:21:31.160 --> 00:21:33.440
and wanted to get some fresh air outside.

00:21:34.030 --> 00:21:35.750
It was raining outside.

00:21:35.830 --> 00:21:37.000
When I opened the door,

00:21:37.000 --> 00:21:38.400
I saw a large plume of smoke

00:21:38.400 --> 00:21:40.790
on the mountain across.

00:21:41.400 --> 00:21:43.270
I thought there was a fire,

00:21:43.640 --> 00:21:45.200
and the shock sobered me up immediately.

00:21:45.200 --> 00:21:47.000
Then I quickly went to find help.

00:21:47.400 --> 00:21:48.270
Back then, I was

00:21:48.350 --> 00:21:50.160
the security chief of the village.

00:21:50.160 --> 00:21:51.920
The old secretary had bad legs,

00:21:52.060 --> 00:21:53.070
so I quickly gathered

00:21:53.070 --> 00:21:54.110
a few people to go up there.

00:21:54.110 --> 00:21:56.240
Thankfully, it was raining that day.

00:21:56.310 --> 00:21:58.000
When we got there, we found

00:21:58.070 --> 00:21:59.200
the house had almost been

00:21:59.200 --> 00:22:00.600
completely burned down.

00:22:00.840 --> 00:22:02.650
Only the frame was left,

00:22:02.680 --> 00:22:03.680
still smoking.

00:22:04.210 --> 00:22:04.960
Is the house he mentioned

00:22:04.960 --> 00:22:05.880
the one you mentioned yesterday,

00:22:05.880 --> 00:22:07.680
the small house on the mountain?

00:22:08.030 --> 00:22:10.070
I was puzzled at the time.

00:22:10.640 --> 00:22:11.640
That house had been vacant

00:22:11.640 --> 00:22:12.520
for a long time.

00:22:12.550 --> 00:22:13.240
It was perfectly fine,

00:22:13.240 --> 00:22:14.510
so how could it catch fire?

00:22:14.510 --> 00:22:15.720
Yes, when

00:22:15.750 --> 00:22:17.110
the fire was put out,

00:22:17.200 --> 00:22:18.310
we could go inside,

00:22:18.400 --> 00:22:19.550
and we actually

00:22:19.640 --> 00:22:21.400
pulled out Xu Qingli.

00:22:22.030 --> 00:22:22.960
At that moment,

00:22:23.030 --> 00:22:24.480
everyone was shocked.

00:22:24.640 --> 00:22:25.960
We just thought about
getting help quickly.

00:22:25.960 --> 00:22:26.960
We rushed to find help.

00:22:26.960 --> 00:22:28.200
When I think back now,

00:22:28.270 --> 00:22:29.640
it was so terrifying.

00:22:30.000 --> 00:22:31.730
Afterward, I led people there.

00:22:32.200 --> 00:22:34.030
No wonder Mazai was scared.

00:22:34.640 --> 00:22:36.270
He was burned black.

00:22:36.350 --> 00:22:37.000
With one more look,

00:22:37.000 --> 00:22:38.270
you would have nightmares.

00:22:38.270 --> 00:22:39.000
Yes, yes.

00:22:39.480 --> 00:22:41.270
He was burned like that.

00:22:41.530 --> 00:22:42.440
How could you be sure

00:22:42.440 --> 00:22:43.370
it was Xu Qingli?

00:22:43.400 --> 00:22:44.920
He left a suicide note.

00:22:45.510 --> 00:22:46.450
It was on the vest

00:22:46.480 --> 00:22:47.680
he always wore.

00:22:47.750 --> 00:22:49.440
It was written in blood,

00:22:49.510 --> 00:22:50.970
hanging on a tree

00:22:51.000 --> 00:22:52.000
next to the house.

00:22:52.350 --> 00:22:54.160
It had his name on it.

00:22:54.240 --> 00:22:56.640
He wrote the Chinese character "Li"
without the hook stroke.

00:22:56.640 --> 00:22:58.750
He said the character
without the hook stroke

00:22:58.750 --> 00:23:00.110
meant lasting success.

00:23:00.310 --> 00:23:01.110
Right, right.

00:23:01.350 --> 00:23:01.880
Right.

00:23:02.270 --> 00:23:03.400
Where was he buried?

00:23:04.200 --> 00:23:05.000
Widow's Hill.

00:23:05.510 --> 00:23:07.480
Women from the village
who have no children

00:23:07.480 --> 00:23:08.440
or whose husbands died because of them

00:23:08.440 --> 00:23:09.640
are all buried there.

00:23:10.590 --> 00:23:12.000
After what happened,

00:23:12.030 --> 00:23:14.200
he couldn't be buried
in the ancestral grounds.

00:23:14.200 --> 00:23:15.200
His name was also removed

00:23:15.200 --> 00:23:16.600
from the family records.

