I'm going to be late.

00:26:47.640 --> 00:26:49.350
The clock at my house is wrong again.

00:26:49.350 --> 00:26:49.970
I thought

00:26:50.000 --> 00:26:51.260
I had half an hour left.

00:26:53.720 --> 00:26:54.960
Aren't you going to be late?

00:26:54.960 --> 00:26:55.880
Hurry up then.

00:26:55.960 --> 00:26:56.480
Yes.

00:26:58.640 --> 00:26:59.170
Baozhen.

00:26:59.830 --> 00:27:00.760
See you tonight.

00:27:25.930 --> 00:27:26.560
Baozhen.

00:27:27.350 --> 00:27:28.960
I thought you weren't coming.

00:27:28.960 --> 00:27:30.490
I was delayed by something.

00:27:36.080 --> 00:27:38.440
"I cannot bear this service;

00:27:38.830 --> 00:27:41.160
to stay idly would be of no use.

00:27:42.070 --> 00:27:44.160
You may go tell your parents,

00:27:44.480 --> 00:27:45.540
and send me home...

00:27:49.310 --> 00:27:50.640
What's wrong, Baozhen?

00:27:51.480 --> 00:27:52.030
My family

00:27:52.160 --> 00:27:54.160
arranged a marriage for me today.

00:27:57.750 --> 00:27:58.590
Who is it?

00:27:59.160 --> 00:28:00.220
It doesn't matter.

00:28:00.440 --> 00:28:01.300
I didn't agree.

00:28:04.680 --> 00:28:05.000
So,

00:28:06.160 --> 00:28:07.420
what are you thinking?

00:28:07.480 --> 00:28:09.410
I've finally seen things clearly.

00:28:10.030 --> 00:28:11.360
If I stay in the village,

00:28:11.440 --> 00:28:13.100
they'll make me marry this man

00:28:13.160 --> 00:28:14.200
or that man.

00:28:15.110 --> 00:28:15.680
Baozhen.

00:28:17.070 --> 00:28:18.200
When I save enough money,

00:28:18.200 --> 00:28:19.310
I'll visit your family
to propose marriage.

00:28:19.310 --> 00:28:19.960
Qingli.

00:28:22.750 --> 00:28:24.480
I want to try my luck in the city.

00:28:25.200 --> 00:28:26.160
In the city?

00:28:28.270 --> 00:28:29.110
How?

00:28:29.750 --> 00:28:30.920
While I'm young,

00:28:31.110 --> 00:28:32.840
I want to see the outside world.

00:28:35.200 --> 00:28:36.720
I want to see what I've got.

00:28:38.000 --> 00:28:39.790
I don't want to spend my whole life

00:28:39.790 --> 00:28:41.510
in this sugarcane field.

00:28:42.160 --> 00:28:43.220
It's meaningless.

00:28:43.960 --> 00:28:44.920
That's good.

00:28:46.480 --> 00:28:47.610
That's a good thing.

00:28:48.160 --> 00:28:49.490
Do you dare come with me?

00:28:50.750 --> 00:28:51.160
Me?

00:28:51.350 --> 00:28:51.880
Sure.

00:28:52.920 --> 00:28:53.680
When?

00:28:53.920 --> 00:28:54.790
Early tomorrow.

00:28:54.790 --> 00:28:55.960
Early tomorrow?

00:28:56.550 --> 00:28:58.480
We'll leave first thing tomorrow.

00:28:58.960 --> 00:29:00.070
That's so sudden.

00:29:03.830 --> 00:29:05.160
I'll go back

00:29:05.680 --> 00:29:07.340
and discuss it with my father.

00:29:08.960 --> 00:29:10.110
It's always my father

00:29:10.110 --> 00:29:11.350
or your father.

00:29:11.790 --> 00:29:13.400
Why do you always need to ask your father?

00:29:13.400 --> 00:29:14.750
I'm asking you.

00:29:14.830 --> 00:29:16.030
I know.

00:29:16.680 --> 00:29:17.940
Of course, I want to go,

00:29:18.480 --> 00:29:20.350
but for something this big,

00:29:20.670 --> 00:29:22.070
I definitely need to discuss

00:29:22.070 --> 00:29:23.000
with my father.

00:29:23.510 --> 00:29:24.240
I think all your studying

00:29:24.240 --> 00:29:25.550
has made you foolish,

00:29:25.960 --> 00:29:28.020
just like Jiao Zhongqing in the book,

00:29:28.160 --> 00:29:29.270
all spineless.

00:29:29.350 --> 00:29:30.880
Always listen to his mother.

00:29:30.880 --> 00:29:32.150
And what's their end?

00:29:32.640 --> 00:29:34.300
One threw herself into a pond,

00:29:34.510 --> 00:29:36.770
and the other hanged himself from a tree.

00:29:37.070 --> 00:29:38.160
Is that what you want?

00:29:38.160 --> 00:29:39.290
I don't want that.

00:29:39.640 --> 00:29:40.770
And I'm not like him.

00:29:41.160 --> 00:29:41.720
Good.

00:29:42.830 --> 00:29:44.560
So are you coming with me or not?

00:29:48.160 --> 00:29:48.680
Yes.

00:29:50.960 --> 00:29:51.890
I'll go with you.

00:30:01.830 --> 00:30:02.310
I'll go.

00:31:47.310 --> 00:31:47.960
Baozhen.

00:31:48.790 --> 00:31:50.130
You're so carefree.

00:31:50.240 --> 00:31:50.960
If I had walked past

00:31:50.960 --> 00:31:51.720
and not seen you,

00:31:51.720 --> 00:31:53.270
how long would you have slept?

00:31:53.270 --> 00:31:53.790
Before dawn,

00:31:53.790 --> 00:31:55.310
I've been waiting for you here.

00:31:55.310 --> 00:31:56.920
The mosquitoes nearly ate me alive.

00:31:56.920 --> 00:31:57.920
Let's go, come on.

00:32:04.480 --> 00:32:05.440
Let me carry it for you.

00:32:05.440 --> 00:32:06.170
Give it to me.

00:32:08.910 --> 00:32:13.430
♪ Your smile ♪

00:32:13.990 --> 00:32:18.460
♪ Is no longer bright ♪

00:32:19.410 --> 00:32:21.930
♪ Or vivid ♪

00:32:22.050 --> 00:32:23.540
♪ Finally ♪

00:32:23.730 --> 00:32:25.980
♪ It transforms into a void ♪

00:32:36.680 --> 00:32:41.100
♪ Your tears ♪

00:32:41.710 --> 00:32:46.210
♪ Refract ♪

00:32:47.330 --> 00:32:49.660
♪ A rainbow ♪

00:32:49.780 --> 00:32:51.250
♪ That disappears ♪

00:32:51.450 --> 00:32:53.660
♪ In my eyes ♪

00:33:03.980 --> 00:33:08.560
♪ On the mountain of childhood ♪

00:33:09.120 --> 00:33:13.680
♪ There are wild flowers and winds ♪

00:33:14.150 --> 00:33:18.280
♪ That rainbow ♪

00:33:19.130 --> 00:33:27.130
♪ Has become an illusion ♪

00:33:27.720 --> 00:33:32.790
♪ Illusion ♪

00:33:34.400 --> 00:33:38.730
♪ Our sorrow ♪

00:33:39.460 --> 00:33:41.130
♪ Is no longer real ♪

00:33:41.130 --> 00:33:43.190
[Beikang Town to Jialin City]

00:33:44.490 --> 00:33:48.720
♪ The tears left behind ♪

00:33:49.500 --> 00:33:57.330
♪ Can no longer refract a rainbow ♪

00:33:57.330 --> 00:33:58.100
Qingli, are you hungry?

00:33:58.100 --> 00:33:59.480
♪ A rainbow ♪

00:33:59.480 --> 00:34:00.200
Are you?

00:34:00.790 --> 00:34:02.050
Then let's find a place

00:34:02.540 --> 00:34:03.040
to eat something.

00:34:03.040 --> 00:34:05.160
♪ A rainbow ♪

00:34:05.160 --> 00:34:06.020
Okay, let's go.

00:34:06.070 --> 00:34:06.600
Let's go.

00:34:11.710 --> 00:34:14.780
[Hao's Stir-Fry]

00:34:15.210 --> 00:34:19.460
[Hao's Stir-Fry]

00:34:21.070 --> 00:34:21.630
Ma'am.

00:34:22.190 --> 00:34:22.860
Two bowls of noodles.

00:34:22.860 --> 00:34:23.480
Got it.

00:34:23.800 --> 00:34:24.960
Just one bowl, one bowl.

00:34:24.960 --> 00:34:25.870
Okay, 3 yuan.

00:34:25.920 --> 00:34:27.179
How is one bowl enough?

00:34:27.360 --> 00:34:28.710
I'm not that hungry.

00:34:29.550 --> 00:34:31.210
Alright, let's go sit inside.

00:34:42.960 --> 00:34:44.150
Eat more.

00:34:44.280 --> 00:34:45.630
You eat it. I'm not hungry.

00:34:45.630 --> 00:34:46.840
Have some more.

00:34:47.360 --> 00:34:48.230
You should eat more.

00:34:48.230 --> 00:34:49.280
You should.

00:34:49.360 --> 00:34:50.800
Alright, alright.

00:34:52.670 --> 00:34:53.840
Just eat.

00:35:01.000 --> 00:35:01.630
Ma'am.

00:35:02.440 --> 00:35:03.590
Do we need to pay
for the pickled vegetables?

00:35:03.590 --> 00:35:04.880
No, they're free.

00:35:16.510 --> 00:35:17.710
Pickled vegetables.

00:35:26.150 --> 00:35:27.110
Qingli.

00:35:27.670 --> 00:35:29.710
We just arrived in the city.

00:35:30.030 --> 00:35:31.960
Things will be tough for a while.

00:35:32.320 --> 00:35:34.250
We should be frugal with our money.

00:35:34.360 --> 00:35:35.670
Once we find jobs,

00:35:36.480 --> 00:35:37.810
things will get better.

00:35:38.030 --> 00:35:39.920
Eat quickly. It's getting cold.

00:35:45.280 --> 00:35:47.280
Things will definitely get better.

00:35:47.760 --> 00:35:48.670
Yes, indeed.

00:35:55.230 --> 00:35:56.030
Xu Qingli

00:35:56.630 --> 00:35:58.230
was like he was possessed.

00:35:59.110 --> 00:36:02.240
Loyalty and filial piety
have long been hard to balance.

00:36:03.360 --> 00:36:05.320
Ignoring Uncle Caizeng's welfare

00:36:05.550 --> 00:36:06.670
is unfilial.

00:36:07.630 --> 00:36:09.200
And he just gave up

00:36:09.230 --> 00:36:10.630
his job at the school without a thought.

00:36:10.630 --> 00:36:11.880
What does that make him?

00:36:11.880 --> 00:36:12.760
Disloyal.

00:36:13.480 --> 00:36:14.960
Mr. Xu would surely be angry.

00:36:14.960 --> 00:36:15.870
Yeah.

00:36:15.920 --> 00:36:17.030
Uncle Caizeng was so furious

00:36:17.030 --> 00:36:18.840
that he smashed almost

00:36:18.920 --> 00:36:20.550
all the pots and dishes in the house.

00:36:20.550 --> 00:36:21.960
So I comforted him, saying,

00:36:21.960 --> 00:36:22.880
"Since the two of them

00:36:22.880 --> 00:36:24.920
haven't come back to the village

00:36:25.000 --> 00:36:26.360
with their tails between their legs,

00:36:26.360 --> 00:36:27.030
it means

00:36:27.110 --> 00:36:29.040
they can still make it in the city."

00:36:30.920 --> 00:36:32.430
Two country folks

00:36:33.360 --> 00:36:35.030
hardly had any education.

00:36:35.550 --> 00:36:36.670
How could it be easy

00:36:36.760 --> 00:36:38.400
to survive in the city?

00:36:38.920 --> 00:36:40.290
They're not mangroves

00:36:40.360 --> 00:36:42.190
that can grow wherever they fall.

00:36:42.190 --> 00:36:43.190
Don't you agree?

00:36:44.630 --> 00:36:46.830
Jobs with room and board are available.

00:36:47.030 --> 00:36:47.960
Not hard to find.

00:36:48.960 --> 00:36:49.590
But...

00:36:50.150 --> 00:36:52.000
But the pay is too low.

00:36:52.550 --> 00:36:53.290
Look,

00:36:53.360 --> 00:36:55.320
these decent jobs

00:36:55.480 --> 00:36:57.110
with slightly better pay

00:36:57.190 --> 00:36:59.590
all require at least
a high school diploma.

00:37:01.030 --> 00:37:02.280
What can we do then?

00:37:04.070 --> 00:37:05.230
It's too late

00:37:05.280 --> 00:37:06.590
to get a high school education now.

00:37:06.590 --> 00:37:08.520
You're still in the mood for jokes?

00:37:08.630 --> 00:37:09.800
I'm serious.

00:37:09.840 --> 00:37:10.730
Staying here

00:37:10.760 --> 00:37:12.190
costs 5 yuan per day.

00:37:12.710 --> 00:37:14.230
We can't keep delaying.

00:37:14.760 --> 00:37:16.510
Then let's find

00:37:16.590 --> 00:37:17.920
some simple job first.

00:37:18.000 --> 00:37:18.880
For a simple job,

00:37:18.880 --> 00:37:19.960
I think

00:37:20.280 --> 00:37:21.740
the Fucheng Sugar Factory

00:37:21.880 --> 00:37:22.760
will work.

00:37:23.030 --> 00:37:24.000
They need lots of people

00:37:24.000 --> 00:37:25.930
and don't have many requirements.

00:37:26.150 --> 00:37:27.680
I heard that the sugarcanes

00:37:27.710 --> 00:37:28.640
from our village

00:37:28.670 --> 00:37:30.070
are all sold to them.

00:37:30.960 --> 00:37:32.280
The sugar factory?

00:37:34.190 --> 00:37:35.000
If you can find

00:37:35.070 --> 00:37:36.800
an easy position, that's fine.

00:37:37.000 --> 00:37:38.630
But if you're handling bagasse

00:37:38.630 --> 00:37:39.550
or stirring syrup,

00:37:39.550 --> 00:37:41.550
you might as well go back to farming.

00:37:42.150 --> 00:37:43.480
So what do you want to do?

00:37:43.480 --> 00:37:44.940
Really go back to farming?

00:37:45.800 --> 00:37:47.000
No.

00:37:48.070 --> 00:37:49.400
Let's keep looking.

00:37:50.510 --> 00:37:51.880
There must be a job

00:37:51.960 --> 00:37:54.220
suitable for an educated person like me.

00:37:54.280 --> 00:37:57.760
"Heaven gave me talents to be put to use;

00:37:58.030 --> 00:38:02.480
Though a thousand coins are spent,
more will come."

00:38:10.270 --> 00:38:14.420
[Civilized Unit]

00:38:17.360 --> 00:38:17.920
Baozhen.

00:38:18.400 --> 00:38:19.150
Qingli.

00:38:20.110 --> 00:38:21.350
I bought some medicine for you.

00:38:21.350 --> 00:38:22.420
Take it after you finish eating.

00:38:22.420 --> 00:38:22.800
Okay.

00:38:23.670 --> 00:38:24.800
Thank you, Qingli.

00:38:25.550 --> 00:38:26.040
Eat up.

00:38:26.070 --> 00:38:27.110
I ordered these steamed buns for you.

00:38:27.110 --> 00:38:27.440
Okay.

00:38:31.630 --> 00:38:32.230
Baozhen.

00:38:33.480 --> 00:38:34.610
I've made up my mind.

00:38:39.450 --> 00:38:40.400
I want to work

00:38:40.510 --> 00:38:41.840
at the sugar factory too.

00:38:41.840 --> 00:38:42.560
Really?

00:38:43.550 --> 00:38:45.080
You've thought it through?

00:38:45.110 --> 00:38:47.280
Whether I like it or not,
I have to face reality.

00:38:47.280 --> 00:38:48.940
We can barely afford the rent.

00:38:49.690 --> 00:38:52.720
That's right. Money gives you security.

00:38:52.960 --> 00:38:54.580
We need to establish ourselves first,

00:38:54.580 --> 00:38:56.040
then find ways to climb up.

00:38:56.630 --> 00:38:57.400
Qingli.

00:38:57.840 --> 00:38:59.030
Earning an honest living

00:38:59.030 --> 00:39:00.560
is nothing to be ashamed of.

00:39:00.760 --> 00:39:01.400
Yes,

00:39:02.070 --> 00:39:03.030
you're right.

00:39:03.880 --> 00:39:05.550
I'll go apply right after this.

00:39:05.550 --> 00:39:06.000
Good.

00:39:07.170 --> 00:39:07.320
[Hao's Stir-Fry]

00:39:07.320 --> 00:39:08.590
Although we won't be in the same workshop,

00:39:08.590 --> 00:39:08.920
[Hao's Stir-Fry]

00:39:08.920 --> 00:39:10.310
I'll still be close to you.

00:39:10.310 --> 00:39:11.360
It's just across the railway,

00:39:11.360 --> 00:39:12.840
in the alcohol workshop.

00:39:13.480 --> 00:39:14.710
That's great.

00:39:14.800 --> 00:39:15.520
I've heard

00:39:15.550 --> 00:39:18.010
the alcohol workshop offers good benefits.

00:39:18.030 --> 00:39:19.480
It's not that great,

00:39:19.880 --> 00:39:21.340
and there's no dormitory,

00:39:21.480 --> 00:39:23.340
so I'll still have to rent a place.

00:39:29.510 --> 00:39:30.880
I'm not really

00:39:31.510 --> 00:39:33.030
a drinker.

00:39:33.110 --> 00:39:34.920
I can't be like Li Bai.

00:39:41.960 --> 00:39:42.480
Qingli.

00:39:43.920 --> 00:39:44.510
What?

00:39:45.150 --> 00:39:46.070
This is for you.

00:39:47.880 --> 00:39:48.550
Take a look.

00:39:56.920 --> 00:39:57.960
This watch

00:39:58.800 --> 00:39:59.860
must be expensive.

00:40:00.000 --> 00:40:01.670
It's not a fancy brand.

00:40:02.030 --> 00:40:03.830
I don't spend much money anyway,

00:40:03.960 --> 00:40:05.360
so I managed to save a bit.

00:40:05.840 --> 00:40:07.250
You always mentioned

00:40:07.280 --> 00:40:09.000
that your clock at home wasn't accurate.

00:40:09.000 --> 00:40:10.800
I thought when I had some money,

00:40:10.880 --> 00:40:12.230
I'd buy you a watch.

00:40:15.110 --> 00:40:16.480
Thank you, Baozhen.

00:40:21.440 --> 00:40:22.840
When I save up some money,

00:40:23.880 --> 00:40:25.150
I'll buy you gifts too.

00:40:25.880 --> 00:40:27.540
I don't really need anything.

00:40:30.590 --> 00:40:31.110
Let me.

00:40:43.630 --> 00:40:44.280
Baozhen.

00:40:44.670 --> 00:40:46.150
Do you think

00:40:47.400 --> 00:40:49.200
we've made our dreams come true?

00:40:59.880 --> 00:41:02.230
I noticed the factory office is hiring.

00:41:02.760 --> 00:41:04.160
I'm thinking of applying

00:41:04.520 --> 00:41:05.630
to change departments.

00:41:05.630 --> 00:41:07.480
I don't want to work
on the production line anymore.

00:41:07.480 --> 00:41:08.440
That's great.

00:41:08.940 --> 00:41:11.000
Working in an office would be easier.

00:41:11.150 --> 00:41:12.750
It's not about being easier.

00:41:13.320 --> 00:41:14.030
I think this way,

00:41:14.030 --> 00:41:15.110
I'll have more time

00:41:15.190 --> 00:41:16.710
to study and review.

00:41:16.800 --> 00:41:18.730
I want to try for higher education.

00:41:21.030 --> 00:41:23.320
Getting into school isn't that easy.

00:41:23.920 --> 00:41:25.650
You don't have the foundation.

00:41:25.840 --> 00:41:27.360
Don't waste your time.

00:41:27.840 --> 00:41:28.510
Dongshan Lamb.

00:41:28.510 --> 00:41:29.280
Thank you.

00:41:33.510 --> 00:41:34.370
Do you remember

00:41:34.440 --> 00:41:35.770
when we first came here?

00:41:36.000 --> 00:41:37.320
It was the same restaurant.

00:41:37.320 --> 00:41:38.450
Even the same table.

00:41:38.670 --> 00:41:39.360
Back then, we

00:41:39.360 --> 00:41:41.150
didn't dare to order anything here.

00:41:41.150 --> 00:41:42.030
But now,

00:41:42.400 --> 00:41:43.510
we can order whatever we want.